dataset link: https://openi.nlm.nih.gov/imgs/collections/NLM-MontgomeryCXRSet.zip

you can download it as a zip file. then you can unzip it and put it in the folder, I mentioned in the code:

this is the data flow in the dataset be like:

dataset/
├── MontgomerySet/
│   ├── CXR_png/               # Chest X-ray images
│   ├── ManualMask/
│   │   ├── leftMask/          # Left lung masks
│   │   ├── rightMask/         # Right lung masks
│   └── ClinicalReadings/      # Extra metadata (not used here)
